item.title: Hello World
item.description: console.log("Hello World"); Verse 1: I’ve seen the world Done it all, had my cake now Diamonds, brilliant, and Bel Air now Hot summer nights, mid July When you and I were forever wild The crazy days, city lights The way you’d play with me like a child Pre-Chorus: Will you still love me When I’m no longer young and beautiful? Will you still love me When I got nothing but my aching soul?
